level_3.manifestation:
Manifestation Roll 1d3: (1) caster’s body takes on a pallid air and his eyes glaze over as his soul is sent into the phylactery;
(2) a crack resounds in the heavens and the air smells of copper and burnt offerings; (3) the caster
crumples to his knees, howling in spiritual agony as his soul is torn from his mortal shell.
